-- Kruul

-- [Remorseless Strikes]
-- Kruul’s melee attacks on his main target spread out to nearby players (ideally split among 13 players). Each player hit by [Remorseless Strikes] gets the debuff [Broken Bones].
-- [Broken Bones]
-- Increases physical damage taken by 10%, stacks indefinitely.

-- [Mark of the Highlord]
-- Every 30 seconds, three players with mana are marked by Kruul, exploding 300 of their mana every 2 seconds. This deals 1300 shadow damage every 2 seconds to nearby players in a 10 yard radius for 20 seconds.

-- [Call from the Twisting Nether]
-- Every 25 seconds, an infernal from the Twisting Nether is called upon Kruul’s target, dealing 800 AoE fire damage on impact.

